item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Taylor Swift - Snow on the Beach & Snow on the Beach feat. More Lana Del Rey
item.description:
Hi, everyone!

I would love to have the stems from these two songs:
Or maybe the instrumental versions and acapellas would be enough.

Taylor Swift - Snow on the Beach (feat. Lana Del Rey)

Taylor Swift - Snow on the Beach (feat. More Lana Del Rey)

So that I could make a version with the missing "it's coming down" outro, and also an extended intro, that is missing on the second version of this song.

Thank you so much!
